UMD program for the post-processing of (ab initio) molecular-dynamics runs

Stable production version v1.0

Naming conventions:
vX.0 => stable production versions
vX.Y => major bug-free improvements
vX.Y.Z => minor improvements, debugging, experimental personal versions

MAJOR AIMS for the v2.0:
speciation: chemical (pair) bonds
speciation: interatomic angles (3-body)
speciation: the second coordination sphere
bubble: estimation of the gas/liquid volume and density

MAJOR AIMS for the v3.0 version:
CPU-parallelization

MAJOR AIMS for THE v4.0 version:
GPU-parallelization

